items.comment: Very nice looking (I've got the Commodore edition ;-)) game, with straightforward rules, which are not too heavy to understand that can be played in a fast pace as actions quickly follow after one other. Game play takes less than 2 hours, which makes it a game easily taken out the shelves. The exploits can make your strategy change every game, although you can play as well without them.
